I"*<p>We are pleased to announce the release of version 1.01 of the hourly drifter product. Now available to download from the Global drifter program <a href="http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/phod/dac/hourly_data.php">DAC website</a>. The methods of interpolation implemented to generate this product are the same as for version 1.00 of the dataset released in mid-2016, see <a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1002/2016JC011716">Elipot et al. 2016, doi:10.1002/2016JC011716</a>. See the <a href="http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/phod/dac/hourly_data.php">release notes</a>.</p>
